<div id="our-values-section" class="section">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <!-- Start Big Heading -->
                <div class="big-title text-center" data-animation="fadeInDown" data-animation-delay="01">
                    <h1>Our <strong>values</strong> and <strong>culture</strong></h1>
                </div>
                <!-- End Big Heading -->
                <p class="text-center primary-paragraph">
                    We borned with a clear and well defined goal, <strong>offer top class services</strong> to our customers<br />
                    <strong>and quality of life</strong> to our consultants. Accordingly, in a result-driven perspective,<br />
                    we bring together customer-oriented approach and IT experts resources.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="row">

            <div class="col-md-4 our-values-widget">

                <div>
                    <h3><i class="fa fa-certificate icon-quality" aria-hidden="true"></i> Quality</h3>

                    <p class="text-justify">
                        We prefer to invest in quality rather than in quantity, expressing realistic
                        and qualitative expansion of our company, 0 debt policy, among others.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 our-values-widget">

                <div>
                    <h3><i class="fa fa-eye icon-transparency" aria-hidden="true"></i> Transparency</h3>

                    <p class="text-justify">
                        We believe that a good communication in the base for a successful business. The collaboration between AkaBI, its
                        clients and consultants is based on a <strong>total transparent approach.</strong>
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 our-values-widget">

                <div>
                    <h3><i class="fa fa-child icon-fun" aria-hidden="true"></i> Fun</h3>

                    <p class="text-justify">
                        At AkaBI, we believe that you should have fun in everything you do. This will contribute to your professional and personal development and fulfillment.
                        Therefore, besides discuss about employees personal expectations, and we often organize some good and fun internal activities, like diners, travels and team events.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="row custom-large-button-wrapper">
            @Html.ActionLink("Join the team!", "Index", "Career", null, new { @class = "btn btn-system custom-large-btn" })
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
